    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in really wonderful shape. It\u2019s been super reliable for me, runs smoothly, and has been well-maintained over the years. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for a dependable ride that still looks great pulling into the driveway. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m excited for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated! Drop me a message if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
