    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained SUV offers the perfect balance of luxury and dependability. The exterior shines in its original pearl white finish, showing only minor signs of careful road use, such as a few small stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the parchment leather interior remains supple and clean; it has been a strictly non-smoking environment, and the rear seats appear nearly untouched. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound, benefiting from a consistent service history at the dealership. We recently completed a full brake service and an oil change, ensuring it\u2019s ready for the road immediately. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the engine provides a quiet, confident ride. Includes two sets of keys and all original owner's manuals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
